snippet.title: Amber f(x) harshly responds to rumors claiming she is pregnant and will give birth in September
snippet.description:
Rumors surrounding the famous tomboy idol Amber (f(x)) claiming that she is pregnant has caused a stir among the public. Shortly after, the singer went on Twitter to speak out about this information.
